title: My 15 Books - March 2014 (gnv64)
description:
Here is a collection of 15 books for this month - 9 ePBs & 6 PDFs.
Covers included in separate folder.
Enjoy reading but don't forget seeding:

01. Abraham Lincoln in the Kitchen - A Culinary View of Lincoln's Life and Times
02. Badass - The Birth of a Legend - Spine-Crushing Tales of the Most Merciless Gods, Monsters, Heroes, Villains, and Mythical Creatures Ever Envisioned
03. Danubia - A Personal History of Habsburg Europe
04. Fabric Paper Thread - 26 Projects to Sew & Embellish 25 Embroidery Stitches
05. Know What You Don't Know - How Great Leaders Prevent Problems Before They Happen
06. Nature's Mysteries - Strange plants, weird animals, and other natural surprises in cottage country
07. The 30-Minute Vegan - Soup's On! - More than 100 Quick and Easy Recipes for Every Season
08. The American Military - A Narrative History
09. Writing Tools - 50 Essential Strategies for Every Writer
10. Zodiac Manager - An Astrological Expose of Everyone in the Office
11. Capstone Coach for Nursing Excellence (2nd Ed)
12. Behavioral Addictions - Criteria, Evidence, and Treatment
13. Visual Time - The Image in History
14. Viral Mythology - How the Truth of the Ancients was Encoded and Passed Down through Legend, Art, and Architecture
15. 500 Calorie Cooking - A Family Friendly Cookbook
